\f0\b\fs44 \cf0 Directions\
\pard\pardeftab720\sl420\sa140\ql\qnatural

\f1\b0\fs42 \cf0 Fill a cocktail shaker with ice. Add tequila, lime juice, and Simple Syrup. Cover and shake until mixed and chilled, about 30 seconds. (In general, the drink is ready by the time the shaker mists up.) Place lime-salt-sugar on a plate. Press the rim of a chilled margarita glass into the mixture to rim the edge. Strain margarita into the glass.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sl340\ql\qnatural

